    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/1fa8fce2a8e3aa649c1e06cef9e4f91a.avif?t=1723824139\" width=500 height=250 /></span><br><br>非常荣幸地通知您，您已顺利通过我公司的考察程序，正式被雷文钛科录用。<br><br>热烈欢迎您成为我们当中的一份子，您需要了解一下日后工作中最重要的部分——R.O.O.T系统。<br><br>R.O.O.T.系统的运作基于一个个单元的排列组合。你将操作单元在操作面板上移动。单元会产生、传递信号；单元与单元也由信号连接、激活。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/c86342abec08b0806caa489d847385dd.poster.avif?t=1723824139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/c86342abec08b0806caa489d847385dd.webm?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/c86342abec08b0806caa489d847385dd.mp4?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但是别忘了，你的时间也不是无穷无尽的；虽然这个“时间”可能和你想象的不太一样。在R.O.O.T.中，你有无限量的客观时间来考虑每一步，你真正有限的就是“步数”。<br><br>就这样，一个个单元就通过信号连接成一条条链路；这些链路又反过来激活了更多的单元。激活的单元又会产生一笔笔收入，目的达到！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/c3fc53b14d00141b450c05d396bee68f.poster.avif?t=1723824139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/c3fc53b14d00141b450c05d396bee68f.webm?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/c3fc53b14d00141b450c05d396bee68f.mp4?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你可以将这些收入攒起来完成任务；也可以用它们购买更多的单元，来扩大你的生产。你要怎么做？都听你的！<br><br>不怕你不赚钱，就怕你不敢赚钱。人有多大胆，单元就有多大产。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/7d6e58b81037d94ee5e69b0873f71ee8.poster.avif?t=1723824139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/7d6e58b81037d94ee5e69b0873f71ee8.webm?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/7d6e58b81037d94ee5e69b0873f71ee8.mp4?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当然，我们保证绝对不会压榨员工的劳动力，不过...不想干了？这边的最优建议是放弃这个想法哦~<br><br>总之欢迎你来到雷文钛科<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/b0a27265928005766bed7fe0b989dbc7.poster.avif?t=1723824139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/b0a27265928005766bed7fe0b989dbc7.webm?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280130/extras/b0a27265928005766bed7fe0b989dbc7.mp4?t=1723824139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
